            <title><![CDATA[【[怒]别侥幸！#吸毒后数年仍能检出# 】#如何一眼认出新型毒品# 新型毒品种类多，隐蔽性强，什么“邮票”“神仙水”“乖乖水”“听话水”都是新型毒品。吸食后可...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[怒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_nu-0ddf642bed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>别侥幸！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92%E5%90%8E%E6%95%B0%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%A3%80%E5%87%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92%E5%90%8E%E6%95%B0%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%A3%80%E5%87%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吸毒后数年仍能检出#</span></a> 】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%80%E7%9C%BC%E8%AE%A4%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%80%E7%9C%BC%E8%AE%A4%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何一眼认出新型毒品#</span></a> 新型毒品种类多，隐蔽性强，什么“邮票”“神仙水”“乖乖水”“听话水”都是新型毒品。吸食后可能会导致断片、致幻等，严重危害身心健康。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8E%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8E%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这才是吸毒前后真实的面容变化#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6CnA1Ep" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
